    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Initialize the contract with Signal's trust root, relay admin, verifier, and treasury.\\ntrust_root_key: 32-byte Montgomery u-coordinate (from Signal's config).\\nverifier_contract: Nethermind Groth16 verifier (stored once, used by register_tee).\\nprotocol_treasury: Stellar address for protocol fee collection.",
